Moon Blasters - PyWeek 17
=========================

Solo entry by Markus 'Archwyrm' Martin
https://github.com/archwyrm/moonblast

This entry is sadly lacking any real gameplay. Time constraints, naturally.
The most interesting feature is probably movement over rough terrain with
"moon gravity".

Requirements:
    Python 2
    Pygame

To play:
    python2 run_game.py

Controls:
    Left arrow - Move left
    Right arrrow - Move right
    Alt - Fire

